  • Constructor Details

    • BarcodeScannerConfiguration

      public BarcodeScannerConfiguration(List<BarcodeFormatConfigurationBase> barcodeFormatConfigurations, List<BarcodeDocumentFormat> acceptedDocumentFormats, boolean onlyAcceptDocuments, boolean returnBarcodeImage, BarcodeScannerEngineMode engineMode, boolean live)
      Constructs BarcodeScannerConfiguration with the given params.
      Parameters:
      barcodeFormatConfigurations - Options for barcode decoding
      acceptedDocumentFormats - List of accepted barcode document formats. Barcodes that decode to one of the accepted document formats will have parsedDocument field in BarcodeItem populated with the parsed document. By default all supported barcode document formats are accepted. If empty, no barcodes will be parsed into documents.
      onlyAcceptDocuments - If true and acceptedDocumentFormats is not empty, then barcodes that don't decode to one of the accepted document formats will be ignored. Default is false
      returnBarcodeImage - If true, the barcode image will be returned in the BarcodeItem Default is true
      engineMode - The engine mode for barcode scanning Default is NEXT_GEN
      live - If true, the barcode recognition will be performed in live mode Default is true
